data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT TO $425,000!! Bring your buyers to this amazing 3 bed 2 bath 1832 sq ft home built in 2021. When you enter this home you are greeted with high ceilings and an abundance of natural light. Beautiful tile throughout the main living area and a custom mantel with electric fireplace.  Open concept with a kitchen that is a chefs dream. All stainless steel appliances and quartz counters throughout this space. The Kitchen island invites guests while you prepare meals. The custom cabinets offer an abundance of storage space and there is a pantry as well. Separate dining area with large windows to offer more natural light. The master suite has double sinks, walk in closest as well as a walk in shower. The laundry room is just off the garage and the garage is oversized to give you plenty of space for your cars and additional storage. Outside you will find a fully fenced yard along with a storage shed for you lawn equipment. The home also comes with a Ring alarm system.  This home is just 15 minutes from the beach and just around the corner from many shops and restaurants.
